er and Sommelier. My journey there was marked by crafting unforgettable wine and beverage programs that perfectly complemented the exquisite dining offerings of this luxurious establishment.\n\n🍇 As a wine enthusiast, I curated a diverse and thoughtfully crafted wine list that catered to a wide range of palates, enhancing the dining experience for every guest. My dedication to quality and innovation led us to achieve the prestigious Wine Spectator Excellence Award—an accolade that underscores our commitment to excellence in the world of fine wines.\n\n🌟 My expertise extends beyond the realm of wines, encompassing all aspects of beverage management. From crafting signature cocktails to ensuring a seamless beverage service, I consistently upheld the highest standards, contributing to The Leela Palace's reputation as a premier hospitality destination.\n\n🎓 Certified as a sommelier, I bring a wealth of knowledge about wine varieties, regions, and pairings to the table. I'm always eager to share my passion through engaging wine tastings and educational sessions, making the world of wines more accessible to enthusiasts and novices alike.\n\n🌎 When I'm not exploring the world of wines and beverages, I'm an avid traveler, seeking inspiration from diverse cultures and cuisines to continually enrich my craft.\n\n🤝Let's connect and collaborate! Whether you're a fellow hospitality professional, a wine aficionado, or someone interested in creating exceptional guest experiences, I'm excited to engage in meaningful conversations and explore new opportunities.", "experiences/3/jobEndedOn": "11-2022", "experiences/3/jobLocation": "New Delhi, Delhi, India", "experiences/3/jobLocationCountry": "IN", "experiences/3/jobStartedOn": "5-2019", "experiences/3/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/3/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4D0BAQGwkae5GR-DfQ/company-logo_400_400/company-logo_400_400/0/1720169248769/the_leela_palaces__resorts_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=SNV1BSJaaT0q-z8O